1. My backend is built on Go and the frontend is built on React/Next.js
2. Im developing on Linux
3. My testing framework is Go's testing package
4. My database is PostgreSQL
5. Never create redundent code and always split up logic instead of everything in one file
6. Always check if a function or Type etc. already exists before creating it
7. Always check if a file already exists before creating it
8. Always check if a directory already exists before creating it
9. Never edit any Files outside of the Users request without any reason
10. Always follow eslint rules
11. Always use pnpm for the frontend